WEBVTT



00:00:00.896 --> 00:00:04.992
This sermon is brought to you by Buford Road Baptist Church.

00:00:04.768 --> 00:00:08.160
the speaker today is Pastor Tony Kahoot

00:00:08.672 --> 00:00:11.488
And we want to be involved in missions.

00:00:12.352 --> 00:00:15.648
We have been for quite some time, many years,

00:00:15.744 --> 00:00:20.000
But there is no doubt in my mind that our church

00:00:19.840 --> 00:00:25.664
Needs to be more active, proactive than what we are in getting the gospel to the regions beyond.

00:00:25.760 --> 00:00:31.296
And in order to do that, we've got to have solid, committed stewardship to do it. Our church

00:00:31.200 --> 00:00:34.656
It needs to be a light in a dark place, right?

00:00:34.656 --> 00:00:36.736
It's going to take all of us

00:00:36.576 --> 00:00:38.944
To be all in for Jesus.

00:00:38.912 --> 00:00:41.440
And so we want to do that.

00:00:41.984 --> 00:00:45.824
As I have said many times, missions is the heartbeat of God.

00:00:47.360 --> 00:00:49.696
We have to reach our city.

00:00:50.208 --> 00:00:52.832
We have to reach the town ahead of us.

00:00:54.528 --> 00:00:58.816
We have to even go beyond those borders. But think about this.

00:00:59.616 --> 00:01:02.784
These people that you just saw in this video here

00:01:04.800 --> 00:01:06.496
How will they hear?

00:01:08.064 --> 00:01:09.888
Unless one is sent

00:01:11.552 --> 00:01:13.024
These people

00:01:13.408 --> 00:01:16.800
around the world in these foreign countries listen

00:01:17.888 --> 00:01:19.968
Some of the most pagan.

00:01:20.064 --> 00:01:21.344
Beliefs

00:01:24.032 --> 00:01:26.880
Unbelievably, we find people

00:01:26.944 --> 00:01:30.624
Worshipping sticks and stones and rocks and.

00:01:31.808 --> 00:01:34.464
They are locked into superstitions.

00:01:34.496 --> 00:01:36.032
Traditions.

00:01:36.960 --> 00:01:39.648
And the only thing that can penetrate that

00:01:40.128 --> 00:01:41.696
Is the gospel.

00:01:43.200 --> 00:01:49.216
The scripture says this and also i heard the voice of the lord saying whom shall i send and who will go for us

00:01:49.728 --> 00:01:51.456
Then said I.

00:01:51.680 --> 00:01:53.120
Here am I.

00:01:53.152 --> 00:01:54.496
Send me.

00:01:55.744 --> 00:02:03.520
That's more than a goose bump. That's more than a good feeling, a good sermon, a good Sunday school lesson, hearing the words to a good gospel song.

00:02:05.088 --> 00:02:07.744
But you think about it this way.

00:02:09.312 --> 00:02:12.768
You may lose a lot of things or give up a lot of things

00:02:13.120 --> 00:02:14.720
In order to find.

00:02:14.688 --> 00:02:16.032
Everything.

00:02:17.056 --> 00:02:19.936
you listen to Pastor Tony Kahoot

00:02:19.840 --> 00:02:25.952
For more information, visit our website at bufordrodebaptistchurch.com
